Package edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.disjoint_set

Class UpTreeDisjointSetForest<E>

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.disjoint_set.UpTreeDisjointSetForest<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements stored in the disjoint set
All Implemented Interfaces:
DisjointSetForest<E>
public class UpTreeDisjointSetForest<E> extends Object implements DisjointSetForest<E>
The UpTreeDisjointSetForest is implemented as a forest of linked up-trees. Using balanced union, DisjointSetForest.union(edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.Position<E>, edu.ncsu.csc316.dsa.Position<E>) has worst-case runtime of O(1). Using path-compression find, DisjointSetForest.find(E) has worst-case O(logn), but over time has worst-case runtime O(log*(n)) [log-star].
Author:
Dr. King
